  <data key="d2">Saran-tin is a type of liner composed of successive layers of polyethylene, Kraft paper, tin foil, and polyvinylidene chloride, providing low oxygen transmission rates.&lt;SEP&gt;Saran-tin is a type of liner for screw caps, made of layers including polyethylene and tin foil, noted for low OTR values.</data>
